Package: tvvarGAM
Type: Package
Title: Estimates time-varying VAR model using GAM
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Laura", "Bringmann", email = "l.f.bringmann@rug.nl", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Jonas", "Haslbeck", email = "jonashaslbeck@gmail.com", role = "aut"), 
  person("Jorge N.", "Tendeiro", email = "j.n.tendeiro@rug.nl", role = "aut"))
Maintainer: Laura F. Bringmann <l.f.bringmann@rug.nl>
Description: With this package one can estimate time-varying vector autoregressive models based on generalized additive models. It uses a regression form, making it easy to use. At the moment it can only handle gradual smooth change of both the intercept and the vector autoregressive parameters.
Imports: stats, graphics, utils, mgcv, mgm, mvtnorm, Rdpack
RdMacros: Rdpack
